EMERGENCY EXITS
The Lockheed Constellation is adequately equipped with
emergency facilities. Emergency exits are illustrated on the
diagram. Near the center of the cabin are removable window
exits.
Placards are at each exit, giving simple and clear
instructions as to ;heir use in the event of an emergency. One
exit door is located in the rear cabin.
All exits are marked
by arrows on the d agram.
The exit doors are equipped with
rapid evacuation slides.
